long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bookmarks for English language learners. All bookmarks are private and do not sync anywhere in the cloud. You have the option to export and import your bookmarks manually. Open oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com and press Command-B (for macos) or Control-B to open the side panel.
